snippet.title: Lost_August_LST
snippet.description:
Now available to wishlist on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2207580/Lost_August

Some footage from my upcoming backrooms game, Lost August.

Lost August is an open world backrooms exploration game created in Unreal Engine 5. Featuring seamless transitions between levels, no loading screens, and a large amount of varied levels to explore. What will you discover once you've fallen into the Backrooms?

Let me know what you think down in the comments below and feel free to join the Discord community!
